The paper introduces mathematical models and algorithms for generating explanations for biomedical queries using answer set programming, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the paper deals with drug discovery, which falls under the category of computational biology (cs.CE).
